},{"pid":"f160c16eabe348fed41c5dddf215897d323ef88e","tid":1524174,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70qf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=f5319ee6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70qf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9c31cb4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70qf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=6b31268f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"ffe457f5eaeafa44a56eb89b7516d0a11cdd730b","tid":1524174,"uid":124097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"氫氣球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40453ca67e32badb2c2f26657898042116bf1af0","tid":1524174,"uid":18250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140203%2F00410_097.html&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70qf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=bd170874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html</a>"}]}